27
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:32,380
(Letter of Appointment)

28
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,700
(Zhang Wencai appointed chairman)

29
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:34,500
You see,

30
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,580
Zhang Wencai wants us
to pay taxes to the Japanese,

31
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:38,540
and the amount is even more
than what we earn.

32
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:40,020
What kind of nonsense is this?

33
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:40,900
Wanyue,

34
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,380
