35
00:01:42,540 --> 00:01:44,260
You must have a plan, right?

36
00:01:44,460 --> 00:01:45,700
He's targeting you.

37
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:47,680
We all followed you
and chose you as chairwoman,

38
00:01:47,690 --> 00:01:48,800
so you must take responsibility.

39
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,420
Alright,

40
00:01:49,540 --> 00:01:50,780
everyone calm down.

41
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:52,420
This isn't entirely Wanyue's fault.

42
00:01:52,620 --> 00:01:54,200
Right now, the Japanese are in charge,

43
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,500
and we're all having a hard time.

44
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:55,900
Hey,

45
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:56,820
how can you say that?

46
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,860
She's the chairwoman,

47
00:01:57,860 --> 00:01:59,300
so she can't just do nothing.

48
00:01:59,300 --> 00:02:00,420
What should we do now?

49
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:01,620
Say something.

50
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:13,460
Zhang Wencai,

51
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:14,780
what do you want?

52
