not yet.

55
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,460
Sato wants to see you.

56
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:33,100
Take them.

57
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:33,660
Wanyue.

58
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:34,180
Wanyue!

59
00:02:34,980 --> 00:02:35,420
Wanyue!

60
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:42,940
(Japanese Army Headquarters
in Jiang City)

61
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:52,780
Mr. Sato,

62
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:58,900
they're here.

63
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,220
Hanyi,

64
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,660
I've heard so much about you.

65
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,380
We finally meet.

66
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:15,780
Please, sit.

67
00:03:33,260 --> 00:03:33,900
Hanyi,

68
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:35,980
take a sniff.

69
00:03:44,380 --> 00:03:45,180
