72
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:55,260
This contains

73
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:56,260
marigold.

74
00:03:57,820 --> 00:04:00,940
My marigolds come
from a farther, warmer place,

75
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:03,100
so their fragrance is stronger.

76
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,660
Even such a subtle difference

77
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:06,140
doesn't escape you.

78
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,360
You truly are
a genius in incense-making.

79
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:09,620
Why have you

80
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:10,500
captured us?

81
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,420
Just say it directly.

82
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:12,780
To be frank,

83
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,260
I've been interested
in Chinese incense culture.

84
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:16,340
I appreciate you.

85
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:17,540
I hope

86
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,460
we can have a private discussion.

87
00:04:34,020 --> 00:04:34,900
Flowery Dew.

88
00:04:34,980 --> 00:04:35,660
Ruoshui.

89
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:36,900
Sophia.

90
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:37,980
Mosquito Repellent.

91
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:39,460
Hanyi,

92
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:42,180
I like every incense you make.

93
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,580
