94
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:46,380
making these is truly beneath you.

95
00:04:46,690 --> 00:04:48,180
You want me to make incense for you?

96
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:49,020
Exactly.

97
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:52,500
I want you to recreate the legendary
lost incense recorded in ancient texts.

98
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:54,140
Only these

99
00:04:54,660 --> 00:04:56,940
are worthy of your talent, Hanyi.

100
00:04:59,140 --> 00:05:00,300
In Legends of Incense,

101
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:01,860
there's mention of a scent

102
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:03,900
called "One Thought."

103
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:06,020
Become a Buddha

104
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,990
(Legends of Incense)
or become a devil with one thought.

105
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:09,300
I'm very curious

106
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:11,380
what kind of scent

107
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:13,580
could be so intoxicating?

108
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:33,740
Hanyi.

109
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:35,500
Hanyi.

110
00:05:41,660 --> 00:05:42,260
